	â€¢	Adjust brightness: Make the lights subtle for relaxing nights or bright for parties.
	â€¢	Real-time control: Changes happen instantly as long as your device is on the same Wi-Fi network as the lights. No delay, no lag.

âš¡ Important things to know:
	â€¢	The app works only on the same local network. Devices outside your Wi-Fi wonâ€™t be able to control the lights.
	â€¢	Some light effects may look slightly different depending on your chosen brightness and color combinations.
	â€¢	The lights stay on the last selected animation until you change them. You donâ€™t need to keep the app open all the time.
	â€¢	Privacy and safety: No internet is required. All communication happens locally on your network, so your data stays private.

